commit.message:
Completely migrate moving unit code from BaseObject to BaseUnit.
It's working better now, I think. There are some bad part in Enemy Manager and such, but it should be OK :/
Small Commit, will try to move all code from base object to base unit to be able to add building. Scary.
Make following ally a bit more smoother.

Add a follow ally function.
Fix tons of other bugs as well.

Fix a bug related to ordering movement.
Also kind of going back, make hero able to move while attacking. This make the game feels smoother.
Fix some navmesh thing and add a wall for our base (and make the enemy cubes pay for it)
Fix a bug relating to object move when not wanted to

Fix dynamic camera.
When I implemented it last time, I didn't consider the fact that the screen is NOT square
Add dynamic camera and fix the code a bit.
Fix high light circle and mana indication circle to make it easier to see.

Add the middle color for the health bar color
Health bar looks a lot better now. Also, fix a small bug
Fix lot of bugs with the special skill systems, change some function and add a mana indicator.

Add special skill for hero and object.
Hero will have special skill to be activated manually by the player.
Also, remove the special ability activation on hero resurrection. It was dumb.
Add a circle around the Cargo Kart to show the activation range.

Add cargo state: the game start with the cargo at base. the user's hero need to stay within the cargo activation range (5) for 3 seconds to active it. Only then, the game would start. Next would be to implement some graphical things to make it easy to see and understand.
add a simple function to make heroes move back to the cargo when he goes to far away
Fix bug: - object health is one level higher than its supposed to be, and fix object weird position after being spawned after dead.
Fix a small bug about shadow not showing and some animation problem. Two hot fixes that I will work on later.
Add a sort of contextual controller, to control when to spawn enemy when to do what, so that I can later make dynamic level and creep spawning based on this.
Add a really nice looking select circle for unit.
add health regen. Make it working.
Fix a lot of bug and also add color changing health bar
Fix and update.
Add a health bar and world position text.
Add corpse pooling.
Add motherfucking object poolings. It's super awesome now. Fuck yeah.
Small code fix and change every serialization into text.
Fix a lot of things. Remove bad codes I made from the Hackathon. The project should be a lot better to work on now :D
Update README.md
Update README.md
